<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                background-color: #f4f4f4;
                color: #333;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }

            .container {
                width: 80%;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 20px;
                background-color: #fff;
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                border-radius: 5px;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }

            h1,
            h2 {
                text-align: center;
            }

            /* About page specific styles */
            .about-blogs,
            .about-owner {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .about-blogs ul {
                list-style-type: disc;
                padding-left: 20px;
            }

            .about-blogs li {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .about-owner p {
                text-align: justify;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

            .about-owner a {
                color: #007BFF;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .about-owner a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
        </style>
        <%- include('partials/nav_style') %>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <section class="about-blogs">
            <h2>Types of Blogs We Write</h2>
            <p>Our website features a variety of blogs that cover diverse topics including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Technology and Innovations</li>
                <li>Health and Wellness</li>
                <li>Travel and Adventure</li>
                <li>Food and Recipes</li>
                <li>Personal Development</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="about-owner">
            <h2>About the Website Owner</h2>
            <p>Hello! I'm [Owner's Name], the creator and curator of this blog. With a passion for [Owner's Passion], I
                aim to share insightful and engaging content with my readers. Whether it's exploring the latest in tech
                or sharing delicious recipes, I strive to provide valuable information and inspiration through my
                writing.</p>
            <p>Feel free to reach out to me through the <a href="contact.html">Contact</a> page for any inquiries or
                collaborations.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>